or the high\u2011season Dec\u2011Jan). The mid\u2011range hotels listed have excellent reviews and are centrally located.\\n2. **Reserve a scooter** online (many providers allow advance payment) to guarantee availability.\\n3. **If you love nightlife**, swap the dinner at Thalassa (Day\u202f1) for a beach\u2011side party at **Tito\u2019s** or **Mambo\u2019s** \u2013 extra \u20b9\u202f500\u2011800.\\n4. **For a romantic touch**, add a **sunset dolphin\u2011watching cruise** from Palolem (\u2248\u20b9\u202f1\u202f200 per person) \u2013 fits comfortably within the remaining budget.\\n5. **Keep a small cash reserve** (\u20b9\u202f2\u202f000\u20113\u202f000) for tips and occasional cash\u2011only stalls.\\n\\nEnjoy your Goa adventure \u2013 sun, sea, spice, and smiles await! \ud83c\udf1e\ud83c\udfd6\ufe0f\ud83d\udea4\",\"type\":\"TextMessage\"},\"inner_messages\":[]},\"name\":\"Travel_Planner\"}", "sender": "Travel_Planner_053ed073-56ef-4d41-97ec-9b5a7272d1b7/053ed073-56ef-4d41-97ec-9b5a7272d1b7", "receiver": "group_topic_053ed073-56ef-4d41-97ec-9b5a7272d1b7/053ed073-56ef-4d41-97ec-9b5a7272d1b7", "kind": "MessageKind.PUBLISH", "delivery_stage": "DeliveryStage.SEND", "type": "Message"}
