ion class to make `error_detail` optional (`error_detail: str = \\\"\\\"`).  \\n\\nApply either fix, re\u2011run, and the Tavily tool should work again. Let me know if anything else pops up! \ud83d\ude80\",\"type\":\"TextMessage\"},\"inner_messages\":[]},\"name\":\"Travel_Researcher\"}", "sender": "Travel_Researcher_053ed073-56ef-4d41-97ec-9b5a7272d1b7/053ed073-56ef-4d41-97ec-9b5a7272d1b7", "receiver": null, "kind": "MessageKind.PUBLISH", "delivery_stage": "DeliveryStage.DELIVER", "type": "Message"}
