2026-02-20 07:06:36 - INFO - 405 -Publishing message of type GroupChatMessage to all subscribers: {'message': TextMessage(id='307149a7-fd89-4512-b03d-af8d182fb679', source='Travel_Planner', models_usage=RequestUsage(prompt_tokens=5691, completion_tokens=254), metadata={}, created_at=datetime.datetime(2026, 2, 20, 1, 36, 36, 609038, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), content='Got it! I’m here to help you with anything travel\u2011related—checking itineraries, confirming attraction details, verifying costs, suggesting hotels, and so on. If you’d like me to review your Goa plan (or any other trip), just share the details you have and I’ll make sure everything lines up. Let me know what you need!', type='TextMessage')}
