an verify (or build) a spot\u2011on itinerary... Please fill in the table below (or just give the info in any format you like).\" So they are asking the assistant to fill in the table? No, they are asking the user to fill in. As the assistant, we should respond with the table and ask the user to provide the info. So we should repeat the table and ask them to fill it. Provide a friendly prompt."}}], "created": 1771551515, "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b", "object": "chat.completion", "service_tier": "on_demand", "system_fingerprint": "fp_a09bde29de", "usage": {"completion_tokens": 518, "prompt_tokens": 6871, "total_tokens": 7389, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": null, "reasoning_tokens": 155, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": null, "cached_tokens": 256}, "queue_time": 0.04589177, "prompt_time": 0.317347879, "completion_time": 1.072099558, "total_time": 1.389447437}, "usage_breakdown": null, "x_groq": {"id": "req_01khwb5q87fq7v0mew5kep6pf9", "seed": 995881803}}, "prompt_tokens": 6871, "completion_tokens": 518, "agent_id": "Travel_Planner_053ed073-56ef-4d41-97ec-9b5a7272d1b7/053ed073-56ef-4d41-97ec-9b5a7272d1b7"}
