er'}
2026-02-20 07:08:32 - INFO - 410 -{"payload": "{\"response\":{\"chat_message\":{\"id\":\"b2ae78a5-9c06-49b3-9bfb-e6dcd54cb7b4\",\"source\":\"Travel_Planner\",\"models_usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":6871,\"completion_tokens\":518},\"metadata\":{},\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T01:38:32.092547Z\",\"content\":\"Sure thing! Just let me know the details of your trip (or paste any draft itinerary you already have) and I\u2019ll validate everything for you.\\n\\n| What I need from you | Your answer |\\n|----------------------|-------------|\\n| **Travel dates** (e.g., 12\u202fMar\u202f2025\u202f\u2013\u202f15\u202fMar\u202f2025) |  |\\n| **Destination(s)** (city, region, or specific places you want to visit) |  |\\n| **Trip length** (number of nights) |  |\\n| **Interests / preferred activities** (beach, culture, adventure, food, nightlife, wildlife, shopping, etc.) |  |\\n| **Budget** (total amount you\u2019d like to spend, or a per\u2011day ceiling) |  |\\n| **Accommodation preference** (budget, mid\u2011range, luxury; any specific hotel chain or amenity you need) |  |\\n| **Transport preferences** (rental scooter, private car, public buses, flights between cities, etc.) |  |\\n| **Any special requirements** (dietary restrictions, mobility needs, traveling with kids/pets, etc.) |  |\\n\\nFeel free to fill in the table directly in your reply, or just write the information in plain text\u2014whatever\u2019s easiest for you. Once I have those details, I\u2019ll:\\n\\n1. Verify opening hours, entry fees, and any booking requirements for the attractions you want.\\n2. Check travel times & distances between each stop.\\n3. Confirm hotel availability & price for your dates.\\n4. Produce a detailed cost breakdown and compare it to your budget.\\n5. Spot any scheduling issues and suggest adjustments.\\n\\nLooking forward to your answers! \ud83c\udf0d\u2708\ufe0f\ud83d\uddfa\ufe0f\",\"type\":\"TextMessage\"},\"inner_messages\":[]},\"name\":\"Travel_Planner\"}", "sender": "Travel_Planner_