preferred activities** (beach, culture, adventure, food, nightlife, wildlife, shopping, etc.) |  |\n| **Budget** (total amount you\u2019d like to spend, or a per\u2011day ceiling) |  |\n| **Accommodation preference** (budget, mid\u2011range, luxury; any specific hotel chain or amenity you need) |  |\n| **Transport preferences** (rental scooter, private car, public buses, flights between cities, etc.) |  |\n| **Any special requirements** (dietary restrictions, mobility needs, traveling with kids/pets, etc.) |  |\n\nOnce you provide these details, I\u2019ll:\n\n1. Verify that every attraction is open, check entry fees, and note any required bookings.  \n2. Confirm realistic travel times and distances between each stop (using Google Maps).  \n3. Check hotel availability and current rates for your dates (via Serper).  \n4. Build a detailed cost breakdown and compare it to your budget.  \n5. Spot any scheduling issues (over\u2011packed days, unrealistic travel windows) and suggest adjustments.\n\nLooking forward to your answers so we can lock in a smooth, enjoyable trip! \ud83c\udf34\u2708\ufe0f\ud83d\uddfa\ufe0f"}], "response": {"id": "chatcmpl-93027c5d-f3e2-4b90-bda0-fb7cc665d977", "choices": [{"finish_reason": "stop", "index": 0, "logprobs": null, "message": {"content": "Sure! I\u2019m ready to validate (or build) a perfect itinerary for you \u2013 I just need a few details about your trip. Please fill in the table below (or write the information in plain text). The more specific you are, the more accurate my review will be.\n\n| What I need from you | Your answer |\n|----------------------|-------------|\n| **Travel dates** (e.g., 12\u202fMar\u202f2025\u202f\u2013\u202f15\u202fMar\u202f2025) |  |\n| **Destination(s)** (city, region, or specific places you want to visit) |  |\n| **Trip length** (number of nights) |  |\n| **Interests / preferred activities** (beach, culture, adventure, food, nightlife, wildlife, shopping, etc.) |  |\n| **Budget** (total amount you\u201